    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180°C/ 160°C (fan)/ gas 4</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Top, tail and roughly chop the <strong>carrots</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
